GK7Q')"> &nbsp;</div></a></div><div class="image-icon"><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/media/podcasts/episodes/Naked__Reflections_22.04.11.mp3" data-title="QAnon" data-audio="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/media/podcasts/episodes/Naked__Reflections_22.04.11.mp3" class="track"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-play" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></div></div></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-title-1"><h3 class="field-content"><a href="/podcasts/naked-reflections/qanon">QAnon</a></h3></div><div class="views-field views-field-created"> <span class="field-content">09 June 2022</span></div><div class="views-field views-field-body"><div class="field-content"><p>Theres a pizza joint in Washington DC where a cabal of satanic child abusers meets to brag about their exploits.</p></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-podcast"><div class="field-content"><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/media/podcasts/episodes/Naked__Reflections_22.04.11.mp3" data-title="QAnon" data-audio="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/media/podcasts/episodes/Naked__Reflections_22.04.11.mp3" class="track"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-play" aria-hidden="true"></span>Play</a></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-podcast-1"><div class="field-content"><a href="https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/media/podcasts/episodes/Naked__Reflections_22.04.11.mp3" download="QAnon" class="ajax-exclude"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-download" aria-hidden="true"></span>Download</a></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-naked-discovery-podcast-ur-1"><div class="field-content"></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-naked-discovery-podcast-ur-2"><div class="field-content"></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-nodequeue-links"> <span class="field-content"></span></div></div></div><div class=" col-xs-12 col-lg-4"><div 